Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.91,0:42:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泄愤于海王星的其它倒霉的卫星身上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and took it out on Neptune's other hapless moons.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.41,0:42:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而这颗任性的卫星究竟是从何而来的呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But where did this headstrong moon come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.13,0:42:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行者2号发回的数据表明\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Data from Voyager 2 indicates...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.13,0:42:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海卫一的密度几乎与冥王星不相上下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that Triton's density nearly matches Pluto's.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.47,0:42:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这表明没有其它规则卫星可以与其攀亲的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This suggests a kinship...that no other regular moon can claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.18,0:42:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀疑冥王星和海卫一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's suspected that Pluto and Triton...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.81,0:42:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双双都是诞生于柯伊伯带的物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are both objects that originated in the Kuiper Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.14,0:42:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外太阳系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The outer solar system...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.19,0:42:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由这些大物体组成\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}consisted of these large objects...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.81,0:42:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上在到处游荡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}going every which way, essentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.32,0:42:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中的一些形成了大行星本身\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And some of them formed giant planets themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.32,0:42:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中的一些被抛得更遥远\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and some of them were tossed out further...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.07,0:43:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了如今的柯伊伯带\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where they sit today in the Kuiper Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.82,0:43:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰撞 吸积乃至捕获都大为减少了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Collisions, accretions...and even captures have diminished...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.24,0:43:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那曾经是行星建材的主要大通道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what was once a major thoroughfare...of planetary building materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.13,0:43:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太阳系历史的早期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Early in solar system history...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.96,0:43:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯伊伯带有非常多的大物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Kuiper Belt had far more larger objects...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.75,0:43:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能聚集了大量的物质其质量相当于50个地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that may have once had a cumulative mass...of 50 Earths...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.22,0:43:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而目前柯伊伯带的质量比一个地球小很多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}whereas the current Kuiper Belt mass...is much less than one Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.39,0:43:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯伊伯带里残留的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's left of the Kuiper Belt...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.81,0:43:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和太阳系本身一样古老\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is as old as the solar system itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.14,0:43:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构成成双物体的物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The material that makes up the binary objects...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.56,0:43:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰撞的碎片 甚至一些地外卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}shards of collisions, and even some alien moons...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.69,0:43:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,40亿年以来没什么变化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}hasn't changed in overfour billion years.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.65,0:43:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人惊异的是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's amazing how really different...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.03,0:43:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外太阳系里的各个卫星真是千姿百态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all the moons of the outer solar system are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.99,0:43:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我对天文学开始感兴趣时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When l first got interested in astronomy...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.41,0:43:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时还是1960年代的一个孩子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as a kid in the 1960s...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.53,0:43:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没有发现任何一颗卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we hadn't seen any of these moons.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.08,0:43:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是你望远镜里的小不点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They were little dots in your telescope...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.95,0:43:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们没有概念\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and so we had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.37,0:43:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们会有怎样的千差万别\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how radically different they could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.16,0:43:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我认为最震惊的事情是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But l think the most shocking thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.50,0:43:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳系里居然有这么多的种类\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}was how, you know, much variety there is...in the solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.13,0:44:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为那震撼了我以及所有经历了那个时期的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l think that blew me and everybody else away...who lived through that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.09,0:44:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们从我们太阳系很冷的外围\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As we travel back home...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.13,0:44:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路旅行回家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the frigid outskirts of our solar system...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.22,0:44:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对宇宙的浩瀚 行星的壮丽充满了敬畏的同时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}awed by the vastness of the universe...and the majesty of the planets...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.35,0:44:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有必要关注一下躲在暗处的小小世界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's worth it to pause and take notice...of the small worlds in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.50,0:44:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些地外卫星曾经一再被认为是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Those alien moons that were once considered after thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.19,0:44:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握着秘密 就等待着人类的好奇心去揭示了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}hold mysteries just waiting...for human curiosity to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.00,0:44:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thanks For Viewing
